    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo quinto, sextodecimo kal. madii,
                        indictione tertia. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Raginmundus"
                                >Raimundinus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petri</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Bonadonna"
                                >Bonadonna</name></persName> iugalis eius et filia quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Gerardi</name></persName>, (…) ubi
                        interfuit notitia <persName><name ref="Brunectus">Brunetti</name></persName>
                        et <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Henrici</name></persName> germanorum
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName>
                        propinquioribus meis, (…) nos ambo insimul per hanc cartulam in
                        permutationem damus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Wido"
                            >Guido</name></persName>, rectori <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206"
                            key="#Hospitals"><rs key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> de <placeName
                                ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                        >Altopascio</placeName></orgName>, ad opus eiusdem ospitalis idest unam
                        petiam de terra que est canpus cum arboribus que esse videtur in loco et
                        finibus <placeName ref="#places/3107">Piciorano ubi dicitur
                            Colognora</placeName>. Que tenet anbo capita cum uno latere in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Travallus">Travalli</name></persName>, et aliut
                        latus tenet in terra suprascripti ospitalis. (…) Eam in permutationem damus
                        et tradimus, unde recepimus a te in permutatione uno stario de grano omni
                        anno pertinente suprascripti ospitali, quod <persName><name ref="Oddolinus"
                                >Oddolinus</name></persName> frater meus iudicavit suprascripto
                        ospitali in una petia de terra que est canpus cum arboribus in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/3107">Miliaciatico</placeName>. Que tenet unum
                        caput cum uno latere in terra <persName><name ref="Usaldus"
                            >Usaldelli</name></persName>, et aliut caput tenet in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ughi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ughi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Anglus">Angli</name></persName>, et aliut latus
                        tenet in via pubblica. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in dupplum (…) et
                        insuper penam argenti optimi libras duas. (…) Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. Signum manus suprascriptorum iugalium
                        qui hanc cartulam fieri rogaverunt, et suprascriptus Raimundinus
                        suprascripte uxoris sue consensit. Signum manus suprascriptorum Brunecti et
                        Henrici germanorum propinquioribus suprascripte Bonadonna qui interfuerunt.
                        Signum manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bonomus"
                            >Bonsomi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Betto"
                                >Betti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> filii eius, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bellinus">Bellini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Corsus">Corsi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Stephanus">Stefani</name></persName> rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam
                        complevi et dedi.</ab>
